      "text": [
        "4076 - وَ قَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"عُدْ مَنْ لاَ يَعُودُكَ وَ أَهْدِ إِلَى مَنْ لاَ يُهْدِي إِلَيْكَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4076 - Imam (as) said:\n\"Visit those who do not visit you, and give gifts to those who do not give gifts to you.\""
        ]
      }
    }
